### Redshift-Specific Notes
- Use `TIMESTAMP` for timestamps, `VARCHAR(MAX)` for variable-length text
- Use `BIGINT` for integer surrogates
- Distribution keys: choose based on join patterns (`dist` style)
- Sort keys: add for frequently filtered columns (`sort` style)
- Incremental strategy: prefer `delete+insert` (Redshift merge is expensive)
- Use `GETDATE()` instead of `CURRENT_TIMESTAMP` for compatibility
